OL,3,CMan sentenced for attacking officers
OL,4,Cwith hatchet outside police station
OL,6,FAlexander Dighton, 28, attacked three
OL,7,Fpolice officers at Talbot Green police
OL,8,Fstation in Rhondda Cynon Taf on 31
OL,9,FJanuary, stabbing one in the leg and
OL,10,Fknocking another unconscious.
OL,12,FHe previously pleaded guilty to 10
OL,13,Fcharges relating to the incident at a
OL,14,Fhearing before the Old Bailey in March.
