OL,7,Fattempted to start a fire by pouring
OL,8,Flighter fluid over the van before
OL,9,Fsmashing the windows of two vehicles
OL,10,Fusing a pole.
OL,12,FWhen confronted by officers, Dighton
OL,13,Fsaid: "I'm fed up, I'm done," before
OL,14,Flaunching his attack. Attempts to
OL,15,Frestrain him using a taser were
OL,16,Funsuccessful because of the body
