OL,6,FThe court heard he swung a pole at one
OL,7,Fofficer, punched one in the head and
OL,8,Fstabbed another in the thigh, narrowly
OL,9,Fmissing his femoral artery.
OL,11,FTwo of the three injured officers were
OL,12,Ftaken to hospital for treatment.
OL,14,FOn being arrested, Dighton said: "I
OL,15,Fhave been damned from birth."
OL,17,FHe went on to admit his actions,
OL,18,Fsaying he was motivated by an anti-
OL,19,Fgovernment ideology but denied
OL,20,Fintending to kill a police officer.
