OL,6,FThe judge said the police officers
OL,7,Fthat encountered Dighton were
OL,8,Fexperienced.
OL,10,FHe added, "Whilst they accept
OL,11,Fpotential violence and difficult
OL,12,Fconfrontations are part of the role of
OL,13,Fbeing a police officer, they were all
OL,14,Fdeeply shocked by the nature and
OL,15,Fferocity of your attack."
OL,17,FChief Superintendent Stephen Jones of
OL,18,FSouth Wales Police said: "I wish to
OL,19,Fexpress my gratitude for the bravery
OL,20,Fand professionalism of our officers
OL,21,Fthat day. It is deeply appreciated.
