OL,6,F"The attack on our officers shows the
OL,7,Foften unpredictable and dangerous
OL,8,Fnature of police work, and the impact
OL,9,Fevents such as this have on officers,
OL,10,Ftheir families, and the community.
OL,11,FEach officer is not just a public
OL,12,Fservant but also a husband, wife, or
OL,13,Fparent, and their families are
OL,14,Fundoubtedly deeply affected by
OL,15,Fincidents such as these that officers
OL,16,Fface daily.
OL,18,F"I want to also recognise the
OL,19,Fdetectives' unwavering commitment
OL,20,Fthroughout the investigation which is
OL,21,Falso commendable.
